zzapper wrote:
> If I call the following script with 
> 
> >vvv me
> 
> It will not list a file say READ.ME but will list READ.me
> 
> function vvv () { 
> for x in *$1*
> do
>       echo $x
> done
> }

function vvv() {
  setopt localoptions extended_glob
  local x

  for x in (#i)*$1*
  do
	echo $x
  done
}

